Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may be inferior compared to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:34.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and Rukia continue to\Nsearch for Rurichiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:37.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,after they disrupt\Nher marriage ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:43.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The search for Rurichiyo goes on with\NShu's help and the support of Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:48.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Kira tracks down Kibune,\Nwho had been acting suspiciously,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:52.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and he comes across Rurichiyo\Nin a Squad 3 facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:59.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, due to Kibune's interruption,\Nhe fails to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:04.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, Kibune was not\Nrecognized as a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:07.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:10.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he reached out to the Kasumiohji Clan\Nand acquired their Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:17.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira confronts Kibune about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I need even greater power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:33.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With that power, I will make\Nevery Soul Reaper recognize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:42.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like you, who have no talent,\Nyet get promoted to lieutenant…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:44.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sweep all of you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you doesn't\Ndeserve to be where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When the previous captain\Nwent out of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:54.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't even stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:01.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerless people like you don't\Ndeserve to stand above me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The killing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you've dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you continue to resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your purpose\Nin coming to Squad 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:24.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was only to become the strongest\NSoul Reaper, there are other ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To show off one's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one must attain a position that is fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:39.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai knows what\Nyou've been doing up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you kill me,\Nyou have no future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kasumiohji Clan is planning to use
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Bakkouto to create a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, with this Bakkouto,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can annihilate all of Squad 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:05.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the goal for you\Nand the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:11.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to know,\Nas you are about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:22.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you take\Nyour colleagues for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys? Colleagues?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never once have I thought of\Nanyone as a colleague!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:49.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.\NThen I can't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:56.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You ridicule the weak,\Nand deceived your colleagues,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:00.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,only seeing them as someone\Nto use for your own ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For me,\Nthe most important thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,having squad members\Nworking together based on trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:12.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you violated that trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exhausted,\NLieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised your body\Nis still holding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:51.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can never become\Nthe strongest Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 31: Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you entered that state,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you were being spun around\Nby the power of that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What…did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What you attained\Nis not real power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:56.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop Captain Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:04.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To Squad 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a responsibility to\Nprotect my colleagues!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:24.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's a difference\Nbetween our resolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:44.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not enough to make up for\Nthe difference in our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me\Nwith force alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:07.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bakkouto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Bakkouto is that thing\Ncovering the Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:33.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is what negated\Nthe effects of my Wabisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears your strength was\Nnothing but a fraud after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,True, my Wabisuke's attack power \Nmay be inferior compared to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not the only thing \Nthat constitutes our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zan Ken So Ki!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:56.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Only through that, and possessing a heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can it really be considered true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not… Not here…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:22.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he become completely\Nconsumed by the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant! Third Seat Kibune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:03.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Squad 3 Lieutenant…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:48.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Captain Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Coordination between each squad\Nappears to be going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\NReturn to your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shusuke Amagai…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His defecting could\Nprove to be troublesome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And…\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I apologize.\NPlease move out of the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed, Soi Fon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How about listening to\Nwhat I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:51.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:56.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Rurichiyo go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:32.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:52.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Ruricchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:55.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the real one is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:01.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. By now, she has most likely\Nbeen taken to another location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! At the arena?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:21.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Kibune guy and\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan really were…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.\NSince when?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined the Kasumiohji Clan\Nwas rooted this deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:34.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nyou guys take Kira to Squad 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.\NYou can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:43.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no longer a matter\Nregarding the succession rites.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:47.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my own subordinates became\Ninfatuated with the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:06.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was faint, but I sensed\Nthe Spiritual Pressure of Kira fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came here,\Nand I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that,\Nwhy didn't you contact me sooner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive,\NLieutenant Abarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:18.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And? What do you plan to do\Nnow that you've found us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm friends with these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this about\Nthings being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like\NKira got hurt as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:38.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Seat from Squad 3 was\Nconnected to the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira uncovered that,\Nand defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time\Nto explain details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a fact that\Nsomething bad is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:53.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got yourselves\Nin a sticky situation. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you're going to be on our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you lend us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our proof of\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan's treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to deliver this to\NHead Captain Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm in no position to…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better suited if you go,\NCaptain Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:30.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm going with Kurosaki\Nto the Kasumiohji mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a high probability\Nthat Princess Rurichiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is inside the Kasumiohji mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that their hiding place\Nhas been discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:47.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no other location for\Na cornered person to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:53.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, as a captain among\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must uncover their objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:57.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kibune was their trump card…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:05.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it means Rurichiyo's life\Nis in danger unless we hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:11.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I will definitely\Ndeliver this to the Head Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:20.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, preparations are\Nready for us to deploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:27.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Captain, we have been receiving\Norders to deploy for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. However…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi Shihoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Won't you hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Head Captain\N gives the order to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no changing of plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:59.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you for\Nan answer right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what do you\Nwant me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show this to the Head Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have him hear what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Ngive us some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Another troublesome character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:03.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya!\NListen to what we have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll hear it when we arrive\N before the Head Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:24.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai… You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:28.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kurosaki!\NLeave this place to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Damn!\N– Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:46.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku!\NI don't have time to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:47.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:51.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to let you go…\Nbut it's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down, Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:19.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like there's\Nany room for discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the frosted heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sever, Raika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the real battle begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It has come to light\Nthat there were
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,suspicious acts of high treason\Nfound against the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:03.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All squads of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:06.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will enter the Kasumiohji mansion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}immediately and secure this evidence!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruffian!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu… Do you know\Nwhere Rurichiyo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of rooms like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:33.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe…the one in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi didn't allow us\Nto go near there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:38.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:43.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ruricchi…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rurichiyo, where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:21.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:24.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai… Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:28.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend got hurt!\NIt's natural to come visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really because\Nyou fell behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:31.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and missed the deployment\Nof your squad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:32.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… That's why, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:37.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancar Encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:40.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we'll be talking about\Nthe blue skies inside Las Noches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:47.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Aizen built this space in\NHueco Mundo to replicate the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:50.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think he only\Nbuilt this on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:52.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:55.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the story is\Nabout to take place here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:57.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd help\Nbuild up the excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:23:58.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because you just\Nwant to appear more often?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:03.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to appear more often,\Ndon't you, Tosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:04.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unpleasant.